description:
Stove fuel to use with any stove that burns white gas. This ultra-distilled fuel is designed to burn clean and prevent your stove clogging.

  • Fuel will last up to 5 years before opening. Once exposed to air, it's best to use it within 1 year. Note: date written on the can is the date it was filled, not the expiry date
  • Contains no additives
  • Contains 946ml
name: MSR SuperFuel White Gas
